macro test file 
   
 debug    on
*
 ghist star.his
 make  sim/control
*
 gfile pz [file]

* check physics
   physi
* check geometry
   fort/file 72 star.ps;  meta  72 -111
   dcut cave x .1 10 10 .03 .03

* fill histigrams
   trig 1000

   title_global $quote([file])
   zone 1 3
   hi/pl 11
   hi/pl 12
   hi/pl 13
   zone 2 2
   n/pl 1.ntrack
   n/pl 1.Nvertx
   n/pl 1.NtpcHit
   n/pl 1.Ntr10

 meta 0; close 72
 exit  
return
         
